OL,3,CMajor incident declared in Birmingham
OL,4,Cover bin strikes
OL,6,FA major incident has been declared by
OL,7,FBirmingham City Council after rubbish
OL,8,Fcontinues to mount across the city due
OL,9,Fto the ongoing bin strikes.
OL,11,FThe council has said they have a
OL,12,Fcontingency plan using limited
OL,13,Fresources to collect from all
OL,14,Fproperties in the city once a week -
OL,15,Fbut actions on the picket line have
OL,16,Fprevented them from doing this.
OL,18,FThey estimate that around 17,000
OL,19,Ftonnes of waste remains uncollected
OL,20,Faround the city.
