OL,6,FThey said the daily blocking of our
OL,7,Fdepots by pickets has meant that they
OL,8,Fcannot get vehicles out to
OL,10,Fcollect waste from residents which has
OL,11,Fmeant that around 17,000 tonnes of
OL,12,Fwaste remains uncollected across the
OL,13,Fcity.
OL,15,FThe council has outlined by declaring
OL,16,Fa major incident, they will be able to
OL,17,Fcarry out the following emergency plan:
