OL,6,FA focus of the major incident will be
OL,7,Fon making sure bin lorries can safely
OL,8,Fenter and exit the council's waste
OL,9,Fdepots.
OL,11,FThe council usually deploy around 200
OL,12,Fvehicles over 8-hour daily shifts.
OL,13,FTheir contingency allows 90 vehicles
OL,14,Fto operate per day but because of
OL,15,Fpickets blocking depots they are
OL,16,Fdeployed much later and therefore for
OL,17,Fshorter working periods.
