OL,4,Cover bin strikes
OL,6,FThey would normally make well over
OL,7,F500,000 collections per week. Our
OL,8,Fstrike contingency would mean 360,000
OL,9,Fbut they say because of depots being
OL,10,Fblocked that they are far below this.
OL,12,FCouncillor John Cotton, leader of
OL,13,FBirmingham City Council, said: "It is
OL,14,Fregrettable that we have had to take
OL,15,Fthis step, but we cannot tolerate a
OL,16,Fsituation that is causing harm and
OL,17,Fdistress to communities across
OL,18,FBirmingham.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
