OL,6,F"I respect the right to strike and
OL,7,Fprotest, however actions on the picket
OL,8,Fline must be lawful and sadly the
OL,9,Fbehaviour of some now means we are
OL,10,Fseeing a significant impact on
OL,11,Fresidents and the city and it's
OL,12,Fenvironment.
OL,14,FHe continued: "Unless we declare a
OL,15,Fmajor incident and deploy the waste
OL,16,Fservice's contingency plan, then we
OL,17,Fwould be unable to clear the backlog
OL,18,Fof waste on the streets or improve the
OL,19,Ffrequency of collections.
