OL,6,F"I want to thank residents for their
OL,7,Fcontinued patience under difficult
OL,8,Fcircumstances and the community groups
OL,9,Fwho have been working hard within
OL,10,Ftheir communities to help with clear-
OL,11,Fup.
OL,13,F"I would reiterate that we have made a
OL,14,Ffair and reasonable offer to our
OL,15,Fworkers which means none of them have
OL,16,Fto lose any money and I would urge
OL,17,FUnite to reconsider their position."
