OL,11,FOnay Kasab, National Lead Officer for
OL,12,FUnite the Union said: "This can be
OL,13,Fresolved through the council making
OL,14,Fthe sensible measure whereby they
OL,15,Fwithdraw the proposals to delete the
OL,16,Fpost, the emergency doesn't need to
OL,17,Fhappen, residents don't need to
OL,18,Fsuffer, the council can simply
OL,19,Freinstate the grade three role and
OL,20,Fpeople can go back to work.
