OL,6,F"There's legitimate and lawful
OL,7,Fpicketing taking place and that will
OL,8,Fcontinue, there are demonstrations
OL,9,Faround the site and those will
OL,10,Fcontinue, we have co-operated with the
OL,11,Fpolice and we will continue working
OL,12,Fwith them.
OL,14,F"The way to resolve the dispute isn't
OL,15,Fby declaring emergencies or by getting
OL,16,Ftough on the picket lines. Nobody can
OL,17,Fafford the pay cuts that the council
OL,18,Fare attempting to put forward here."
