OL,6,FA Government spokesperson said: "The
OL,7,Fwaste dispute in Birmingham is causing
OL,8,Fmisery and disruption to residents and
OL,9,Fso we are urging for an immediate
OL,10,Fagreement to be made.
OL,12,F"It is right that this continues to be
OL,13,Fa locally led response, as is usual in
OL,14,Fthe case of council-run services.
OL,16,F"But we are monitoring the situation
OL,17,Fclosely and will not hesitate to act
OL,18,Fshould the council require additional
OL,19,Fsupport."
